headline: Should You Invest $1,000 in Kinder Morgan Today?
summary: Kinder Morgan pays a 4%-yielding dividend backed by very stable cash flows.  The company has seen a surge in new growth projects, fueled by accelerating natural gas demand.  It could capture even more expansion opportunities in the future.
